7mm thick rubber sleeve HOW THE FLOODGATES ARE INSTALLED Place Floodgate between the doorway and expand the jack by using a ratchet wrench to lock in the barrier horizontal­ly. Use the wrench to tighten the four bolts at the bottom, to lock in the barrier vertically. After the flood has receded, loosen the four bottom bolts and compress the jack to remove the Floodgate from the doorway. 1 2 3 Each set of PFB consists of
